snippet.title: Serie A
snippet.description: Welcome to the Official Serie A channel. Over the season, we are going to produce and upload more than 5000 clips, updated everyday with Official Highlights, Magazine & Compilations (such as Best Saves, Numbers, Top 11, etc), Exclusive Interviews, Press Conferences and much more. If you are a football fan and you want to be part of our community don't forget to subscribe to Serie A channel.
